</description><media:thumbnail url="https://s.rfi.fr/media/display/2a4af074-038f-11ec-887b-005056bf30b7/w:1024/p:16x9/AP21234754238478.jpg"/><enclosure url="https://s.rfi.fr/media/display/2a4af074-038f-11ec-887b-005056bf30b7/w:1024/p:16x9/AP21234754238478.jpg" type="image/jpeg" length="0"/><guid isPermaLink="false">6678bef0-038f-11ec-9b59-005056bf762b</guid><pubDate>Sun, 22 Aug 2021 21:24:55 GMT</pubDate><source url="https://s.rfi.fr/media/display/2a4af074-038f-11ec-887b-005056bf30b7/w:1024/p:16x9/AP21234754238478.jpg">© AP - Manuel Balce Ceneta攝影</source><dc:creator>呢喃</dc:creator></item><item><category>中國</category><title>研究報告：中國出口高端工業產品給德國出口帶來壓力</title><link>https://www.rfi.fr/tw/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B/20210822-%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E5%A0%B1%E5%91%8A-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%87%BA%E5%8F%A3%E9%AB%98%E7%AB%AF%E5%B7%A5%E6%A5%AD%E7%94%A2%E5%93%81%E7%B5%A6%E5%BE%B7%E5%9C%8B%E5%87%BA%E5%8F%A3%E5%B8%B6%E4%BE%86%E5%A3%93%E5%8A%9B</link><description>
