</description><media:thumbnail url="https://s.rfi.fr/media/display/a573a0a8-0389-11ec-ae65-005056a90284/w:1024/p:16x9/AP21234512041204.jpg"/><enclosure url="https://s.rfi.fr/media/display/a573a0a8-0389-11ec-ae65-005056a90284/w:1024/p:16x9/AP21234512041204.jpg" type="image/jpeg" length="0"/><guid isPermaLink="false">33fe19a2-038a-11ec-8a03-005056bf762b</guid><pubDate>Sun, 22 Aug 2021 20:47:42 GMT</pubDate><source url="https://s.rfi.fr/media/display/a573a0a8-0389-11ec-ae65-005056a90284/w:1024/p:16x9/AP21234512041204.jpg">© AP供圖</source><dc:creator>呢喃</dc:creator></item><item><category>生態</category><title>剛果(金):南基伍暫停多家中國礦企</title><link>https://www.rfi.fr/tw/%E7%94%9F%E6%85%8B/20210822-rfi-%E6%B3%95%E5%BB%A3-%E5%B0%BC%E5%8F%A4%E6%8B%89-chine-%E5%8E%9F%E6%9D%90%E6%96%99-%E5%89%9B%E6%9E%9C-%E9%87%91-%E5%8D%97%E5%9F%BA%E4%BC%8D%E6%9A%AB%E5%81%9C%E5%A4%9A%E5%AE%B6%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E7%A4%A6%E4%BC%81</link><description>
